            <p>On the dancers see Robert, loc.cit; W. Slater, Orchestopala, ZPE 84 (1990) <ref target="https://www.uni-koeln.de/phil-fak/ifa/zpe/downloads/1990/084pdf/084215.pdf">215-220</ref>, 
